Package com.qtplaf.library.trading.data

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DataListListener
    Listens to data lists changes add, remove, set and clear.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Data
    Base class of timed data.
    DataList
    A list of data objects.
    DataListEvent
    Events launched by data lists.
    DataPersistor
    A persistor for elements of timed Data.
    DataRecordSet
    A recordset of time series data.
    DelegateDataList
    A delegate data list, used when a copy of the datalist with a different data info is required.
    Indicator
    Indicator base class.
    IndicatorDataList
    A data list that retrieves its data from an indicator, thus calculating the data each time it is retrieved through the get method.
    IndicatorSource
    Indicator data source.
    IndicatorUtils
    Indicator utilities.
    Instrument
    Financial instrument definition.
    Period
    Periods of trading.
    PersistorDataList
    A data list that retrieves its data from persistor.
    PlotData
    A container for the data to plot in a JChartContainer.
    Tick
    Tick data.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    DataListEvent.Operation
    Enumerates the operations on the data list that are notified, mainly those that modify the list.
    DataType
    Enumerates the data types of a chart.
    Filter
    Enumerates the filters applicable to price data.
    PlotScale
    Enumerate the different plot scales supported.
    PlotType
    Enumerates the types of plots, line, bar, candlestick and histogram.
    Unit
    Units used to define periods of aggregate incoming quotes.
